  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E (At blocker timing, by suspending this
    Digimon, it becomes the attack target)[When Digivolving] If [MetalGarurumon]
    or [X Antibody] is in this Digimon's digivolution cards, until the end of your
    opponent's turn, all of their Digimon gain \"[When Attacking] Lose 4 memory\".[When
    Attacking] By returning 1 Digimon card from your trash to the bottom of the deck,
    delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon with the same level as that card."
